<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LinearLayout
    xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:id="@+id/main"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:orientation="vertical"
    android:background="#050526"
    tools:context=".About">

    <TextView
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:textAlignment="center"
        android:text="About Us"
        android:fontFamily="times new roman"
        android:textSize="42sp"
        android:textColor="#fff"
        android:textStyle="bold"/>

    <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent"
        android:layout_marginTop="2dp"
        android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
        android:layout_marginRight="10dp"
        app:cardCornerRadius="16dp"
        app:cardElevation="15dp"
        android:padding="10dp">

        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            android:orientation="vertical"
            android:layout_margin="10dp"
            android:padding="10dp"
            android:background="#f7f9ea">

            <TextView
                android:id="@+id/aboutTxt"
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:fontFamily="times new roman"
                android:text="Welcome to K-Mart – 'Your Neighborhood’s Heartbeat'.
                In a world that seems to move faster every single day, we believe that shopping for your daily essentials shouldn't feel like a marathon. At [Mini Mart Name], we have redefined the convenience store experience by blending the efficiency of a modern retailer with the warm, personalized touch of a traditional corner shop. Founded on the principle that 'small is beautiful', we are proud to be the go-to destination for our community, providing high-quality products, fresh selections, and friendly service right where you live and work."
                android:textColor="#0B0A0A"
                android:textSize="13dp" />

            <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:id="@+id/aboutTxt2"
                android:text="Our Story: Rooted in Community

                       The journey of K-Mart began with a simple observation: people were tired of navigating massive parking lots and endless aisles just to pick up a carton of milk or a fresh snack. We saw a need for a curated shopping experience—a place where the staff knows your name, the produce is always crisp, and you can get in and out without the stress of a 'big box' environment.What started as a small family vision has grown into a cornerstone of the neighborhood. We aren't just a business; we are your neighbors. We’ve seen kids grow up, celebrated local milestones, and been there through every rainy Tuesday and sunny Sunday. Our growth has been fueled entirely by the trust and loyalty of the people we serve, and for that, we are eternally grateful.

            The K-Mart Difference:
            What sets us apart from the average convenience store? It’s our commitment to quality over quantity. We don't believe in stocking thousands of items just to fill shelves. Instead, we hand-pick every product that enters our doors.Freshness First: We partner with local farmers and regional suppliers to ensure that our fruits, vegetables, and dairy products are as fresh as they can be. From morning coffee to evening ingredients, quality is never compromised.

            Curated Convenience: We understand your busy lifestyle. Our layout is designed for speed and ease, ensuring that you find exactly what you need—from household staples and pantry essentials to gourmet treats and cold beverages—within minutes.

            Support Local: We are firm believers in 'Local Supporting Local.' That’s why you’ll find a dedicated section of our store featuring artisanal goods, snacks, and crafts produced by creators right here in our region.

            A Friendly Face: Technology is great, but it can’t replace a genuine smile. Our team members are trained to be more than just cashiers; they are ambassadors of hospitality. Whether you need help finding an ingredient or just want to chat about the weather, we’re here for you.
"
                android:textColor="#0B0A0A"
                android:textSize="13dp"
                android:fontFamily="times new roman"
                />

            Our Core Values
            Our business is built on a foundation of four key pillars that guide every decision we make:

            Integrity: We provide fair pricing and honest products. You can trust that what you buy at [Mini Mart Name] is safe, reliable, and worth every penny.

            Sustainability: We are constantly looking for ways to reduce our footprint. From minimizing plastic waste to optimizing our energy use, we strive to keep our neighborhood clean and green for future generations.

            Inclusivity: Everyone is welcome at our mart. We strive to stock a diverse range of products that cater to various dietary needs, cultural preferences, and lifestyles.

            Agility: We listen to our customers. If there is a product you want to see on our shelves, tell us! We pride ourselves on being able to adapt quickly to the needs of our community.

            Looking Toward the Future
            As we look ahead, our mission remains unchanged: to be the most reliable, friendly, and convenient part of your day. We are constantly innovating—whether it’s through expanding our organic selections, introducing "grab-and-go" healthy meal kits, or enhancing our loyalty programs to give back to those who support us.

            At the end of the day, [Mini Mart Name] isn't just about the goods on the shelves. It’s about the people who walk through our doors. We invite you to stop by, say hello, and experience a better way to shop.

            Thank you for making us a part of your home.

            ~ K-Mart

            <Button
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:backgroundTint="#21AD09"
                android:layout_marginTop="35dp"
                android:id="@+id/btnlisten"
                android:textSize="24sp"
                android:text="🎙️ More About Us"
                android:layout_marginRight="35dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="35dp"
                android:fontFamily="times new roman"
                />

        </LinearLayout>


    </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>

</LinearLayout>